{"tid":636634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"四方帽殺傷力驚人！拋高落下可輕鬆切西瓜","createTime":"2018-04-21T05:18:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T15:44:51.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"e3b8a868ba24343cb6e1915f708a3ec04371511d","tid":636634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20180421/photo/bkncn-20180421051532949-0421_05011_001_01p.jpg?20180421062318\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180421%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20180421051532949-0421_05011_001_01p.jpg%3F20180421062318&h=850e7fe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n04月21日(六) 05:15  <br />\n更多新聞短片<br />\n<br />\n大學畢業時不少人都愛拋高四方帽，但原來一不小心，隨時可能惹來血光之災。內地男星李晨周一（16日）錄影綜藝節目時，竟不慎被跌下來的四方帽擊傷額頭。事件惹起網民熱議，有內地電視台為此做實驗，發現四方帽竟能切開西瓜，建議學生在拋帽時要格外小心，免得樂極生悲。 <br />\n<br />\n從片段可見，地上放了幾個西瓜，戴上安全帽的測試人員重複多次抛高四方帽，均能輕鬆切開西瓜，甚至能深深插在西瓜上。 <br />\n<br />\n據悉，四方帽內通常墊有一塊厚2厘米的硬膠板，雖然不算太重，但因又薄又利，加上落下時的重力和速度，只要角度對準，落下時打中頭部，很可能致人受傷。"},{"pid":"07f66a34abb64ab88404b1b30b261a3141c05744","tid":636634,"uid":36544,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:28:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/21/132757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F21%2F132757_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=6fb9e2c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n集體自殺"},{"pid":"e388602a0101b93341e003710d8fde0fefc5d5b1","tid":636634,"uid":52605,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:40:23.000Z","msg":"一頂帽可以傷到人甚至殺人<br />\n你諗唔到既野都爆炸<br />\n呢個國家都算奇芭葩"},{"pid":"0680fb64a0bf85676d822c83482c2e99d46b355b","tid":636634,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:43:10.000Z","msg":"所以話有四方帽都唔知是禍定是福。"},{"pid":"d18b455d7fdd8aaffe84fc00f7814799cff9cdd8","tid":636634,"uid":59363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T05:47:35.000Z","msg":"2厘米厚？？？？？"},{"pid":"16cb24620fd1894685ee82a7b37310d452810c98","tid":636634,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:16:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f542773dc3dd663b7d081fca9d8a75aa5a6ff694","tid":636634,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fe9cabf5735fd3c01bc93c9acc6130ddfbb40543","tid":636634,"uid":47359,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f542773dc3dd663b7d081fca9d8a75aa5a6ff694","tid":636634,"uid":164913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:21:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-21T15:44:51.000Z","msg":"五毛諦聽多次開post幫黑警洗底<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/602826/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/602826/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"}]}